    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower Collapse is a new twist on a classic party game. Take turns to remove blocks from the tower while the camera spins. The more turns are taken, the more unstable the tower becomes and the faster the camera spins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Singleplayer and aim for the trophy scores, otherwise compete in VS Computer or Multiplayer 1v1 modes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer vs trophy high scores <strong>(NEW)</strong>, singleplayer vs PC <strong>(NEW)</strong>, or local multiplayer mode (2 player)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two game modes - classic mode and block push mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 levels to choose from: House, Beach, Monument, Museum and City</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 alternate levels with different tower layouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reduced movement option, say goodbye to motion sickness</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW:</strong> Character portraits! Choose your character - Octopus, Crab or Otter! Watch them react to gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW:</strong> Steam Achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NEW:</strong> Improved music for all levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
